{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a world devastated by <strong>hunger</strong>, where even the wealthiest have nothing to eat, humanity has resorted to <strong>cannibalism</strong> to survive. The first <strong>victims</strong> were the elderly and those who were not skilled enough to defend themselves. Next, in the list of the weak, comes the turn of the <strong>children</strong>. They are easy prey for adults: slow, trusting, and lacking the strength and malice their hunters possess. The adults, accustomed to previous killings, have lost any trace of humanity and are desperately hunting them down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this context, <strong>Hansel and Gretel</strong> are abandoned by their father to avoid temptation. <strong>Gretel</strong>, the elder and responsible sibling, must find a way to <strong>survive</strong> and a safe path back <strong>home</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survival</strong>: Resources are limited and must be managed wisely. Collect apples, stones, and other weapons to face enemies and survive.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fight or Flee</strong>: Even if you\u2019re at a disadvantage, you\u2019re not defenseless. Use any weapons at hand or run when there\u2019s no other choice.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Stealth</strong>: Hide behind bushes and structures to avoid detection, distract enemies, and infiltrate to collect loot.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Status</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is currently in beta.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3333470?t=1732738990","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepageba